Upstream has NO single combined master CLIF file; the normative first-order
axiomatization is modularized into separate .cl files. bfo/bfo-2020.clif is the
verbatim concatenation of the 13 core normative modules (in dependency order),
each preceded by a "--- MODULE: <path> ---" marker. The non-normative
profiles/ (temporalized-relations.cl) and contributions/ (allen-relation-
definitions.cl) directories, plus README/release-notes, were intentionally excluded.

